hormones, menstrual cycles,

36
00:02:02,050 --> 00:02:07,000
illnesses, problems with your thyroid,
ovulation, drugs, and many other things.

37
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:10,480
But the bottom line is that your body
works hard to keep core temperature in

38
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:15,120
a relatively tight range when possible for
optimal functioning of body systems.

39
00:02:16,570 --> 00:02:18,960
Heat gain comes from two sources.

40
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:22,560
The internal generation of heat and the
heat from the environment.

41
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:27,440
