164
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:51,940
The result is that warm blood from the
core of your body stays more in the core.

165
00:09:51,940 --> 00:09:54,450
Therefore, you lose less heat to the
surface of your body and

166
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:55,540
